nd shared vision demonstrated during this meeting underscore the commitment of all parties involved to safeguarding marine biodiversity and fostering sustainable development.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The ASEAN ENMAPS project is implemented by the UNDP and funded by the Global Environment Facility (GEF), with ACB serving as the executing agency. This initiative represents a significant step forward in regional cooperation for marine conservation and sustainable management.</span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]', 'ASEAN ENMAPS Kickstarts with Pre-Inception Technical Workshop in Davao City', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '384-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-08-29 08:30:22', '2024-08-29 08:30:22', '', 384, 'http://localhost/enmaps/?p=387', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
